interpretation: The carpentry saw emoji represents the act of cutting away the unnecessary in order to create something new. It signifies the importance of hard work, precision, and attention to detail. This card reminds us that we have the power to shape our lives and that sometimes we need to make difficult cuts in order to achieve our goals. The carpentry saw also speaks to the idea of transformation, as we must break down old patterns and habits in order to build something new. This card can also symbolize the need to seek out help or guidance from those with more experience or expertise, as well as the importance of being patient and taking the time to do things right.
